an class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecProof\">SpecProof</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The spec proofs a `@[spec]` constant contributes to the database: the constant itself for a\n`Triple`/`⊑ wp` spec, the equation itself for an equational spec, or its equation lemmas for a\ndefinition registered to unfold. Mirrors `addSimpSpecTheoremsFromConst` so `[-foo]` erases exactly\nthe entries that annotating `foo` inserted.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.specEraseProofs","kind":"def","line":546,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.specEraseProofs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L546-L561"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension.addSimpSpecTheoremsFromConst\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecExtension</span>.<span class=\"name\">addSimpSpecTheoremsFromConst</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ext</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension\">SpecExtension</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">prio</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">attrKind</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Attributes.html#Lean.AttributeKind\">AttributeKind</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Register the equational lemmas of a `@[spec]`-annotated declaration as `.simp` entries with the\ngiven priority. An equational proposition is registered directly; a definition is registered via its\nequation lemmas (`getEqnsFor?`). Anything else throws, since it cannot serve as a `vcgen` spec.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension.addSimpSpecTheoremsFromConst","kind":"def","line":528,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension.addSimpSpecTheoremsFromConst","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L528-L544"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromSimpDecl?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSpecTheoremFromSimpDecl?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">prio</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Create a `SpecTheorem` from a simp/equational declaration `declName : ∀ xs, lhs = rhs`, keyed on the\nLHS. Function-level equations (e.g. class projection unfold lemmas) are eta-expanded so the\ndiscrimination-tree key includes all arguments. Returns `none` for no-op equations whose LHS key is\nsyntactically the RHS.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromSimpDecl?","kind":"def","line":512,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromSimpDecl?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L512-L526"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromStx\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSpecTheoremFromStx</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ref</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">proof</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">prio</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> := <span class=\"fn\">1000</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromStx","kind":"def","line":480,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromStx","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L480-L482"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecTheoremFromLocal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSpecTheoremFromLocal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">fvar</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.FVarId\">FVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">prio</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> := <span class=\"fn\">1000</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","