href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecPatternFromExpr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSpecPatternFromExpr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">expr</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">levelParams</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Pattern.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern\">Meta.Sym.Pattern</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Builds a `Sym.Pattern` keyed on the program selected by `selectProg` from a spec conclusion.\nThe conclusion is assumed to already be a valid spec shape (checked by the caller via `selectProg`);\na non-spec shape reaching here is a logic error and throws.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecPatternFromExpr","kind":"def","line":448,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.mkSpecPatternFromExpr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L448-L459"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.selectProg\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">selectProg</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Selects the program a spec conclusion is keyed on: the program of a `Triple`, or the program inside\nthe `wp` on the RHS of a `pre ⊑ wp …` entailment. Returns `none` if `type` is neither shape — e.g. a\nbare `lhs ⊑ rhs` whose RHS is not a `wp` application (an invariant entailment such as\n`(I n h).inv … ⊑ Q n r.2`, which can appear as an ordinary hypothesis but is not a spec). Callers use\n`none` to skip such non-spec hypotheses instead of failing.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.selectProg","kind":"def","line":429,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.selectProg","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L429-L446"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.progArgIdx?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">progArgIdx?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The application-argument index of `declName`'s program parameter `x`, read from its signature. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.progArgIdx?","kind":"def","line":421,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.progArgIdx?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L421-L427"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.eraseUnusedVarsFromPattern\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseUnusedVarsFromPattern</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Pattern.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern\">Meta.Sym.Pattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Pattern.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern\">Meta.Sym.Pattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Drops pattern variables that the pattern expression does not depend on.\n\n`Sym.mkPatternFromExprWithKey`/`Sym.mkPatternFromDeclWithKey` turn *every* leading `∀`-binder of the\nsource type into a pattern variable, even binders the selected key (e.g. the program of a `Triple`\nconclusion) never mentions. During matching those variables only ever become fresh metavariables\n(see `Sym.mkPreResult`); for instance binders they additionally trigger spurious `trySynthInstance`\ncalls. This keeps only the variables that the pattern expression references, together with the\ntransitive closure of variables their types depend on, and renumbers the remaining de Bruijn\nindices. `varInfos?` and `checkTypeMask?` are filtered to the surviving telescope; `fnInfos`,\n`levelParams`, and the discrimination-tree key are unchanged because the pattern expression's\nstructure is untouched (bound variables are wildcards in the key).\n\n**Important:** only use this when the matched arguments are *not* reused to rebuild a proof term,\nas `Sym.BackwardRule`/`Sym.mkValue` do — dropping variables would drop arguments those need. It is\nmeant for databases such as `vcgen`'s spec table, where the proof is re-elaborated independently\nof the pattern.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.eraseUnusedVarsFromPattern","kind":"def","line":365,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.eraseUnusedVarsFromPattern","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L365-L419"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecExtension</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension","kind":"def","line":363,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecExtension","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L363-L363"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.erase\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecTheorems</span>.<span class=\"name\">erase</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">thmId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecProof\">SpecProof</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.erase","kind":"def","line":360,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.erase","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L360-L361"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.isErased\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecTheorems</span>.<span class=\"name\">isErased</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">thmId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecProof\">SpecProof</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.isErased","kind":"def","line":357,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.isErased","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L357-L358"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.insert\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecTheorems</span>.<span class=\"name\">insert</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecTheorem</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.insert","kind":"def","line":354,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.insert","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L354-L355"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.instInhabitedSpecTheorems\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">SpecAttr</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedSpecTheorems</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems\">SpecTheorems</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.instInhabitedSpecTheorems","kind":"instance","line":352,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.instInhabitedSpecTheorems","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.lean#L352-L352"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorems.erased\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.